6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Narrato and ShortlyAI share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Short Form. Where Narrato pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Seo Tools and Templates and Tone Control and Plagiarism Check and Api Access and Team Collaboration, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Narrato holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while ShortlyAI scores 5/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Narrato offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $36/mo, compared to ShortlyAI's starting price of $79/mo. Narrato has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. ShortlyAI does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
